  <div class="wrap">
    <header class="hero">
      <div class="eyebrow"><a href="/milkman/invoices">Invoices</a></div>
      <h1>Paste invoice</h1>
      <p class="lede">Copy the invoice page from the milkman website and paste it below.</p>
    </header>

    <form method="POST" action="/milkman/invoices/parse">
      <div style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:1rem;max-width:56rem;">
        <label>
          Invoice text<br>
          <textarea
            name="rawText"
            rows="24"
            required
            placeholder="Invoice #: 39875277&#10;Receipt date: 12/06/2026&#10;Paid&#10;Tuesday, 9 June 2026&#10;Item&#9;Qty&#9;Total&#10;..."
            style="width:100%;padding:.5rem .6rem;font-family:monospace;font-size:.85em;resize:vertical;"
          ></textarea>
        </label>
        <div>
          <button type="submit" class="btn">Parse invoice</button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </form>

    <div class="index-label" style="margin-top:2rem;">How to copy</div>
    <div class="module" style="display:block;max-width:56rem;">
      <div class="desc">
        1. Open your invoice on the milkman website.<br>
        2. Select all the text on the page (Ctrl+A / Cmd+A).<br>
        3. Copy (Ctrl+C / Cmd+C).<br>
        4. Paste into the box above.<br>
        5. Hit <strong>Parse invoice</strong> — you'll get a chance to review and correct product matches before anything is saved.
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
